---
// A deliberate statement banner shown ONLY to visitors using Yandex Browser
// (a Russian browser). GitHub Pages is static — there's no server to read the
// User-Agent — so detection is client-side: Yandex Browser injects the token
// "YaBrowser" into navigator.userAgent. The banner ships hidden and an inline
// script reveals it for those visitors, so everyone else never sees or pays for
// it. Bilingual (EN + UA) on purpose: the message should be unmistakable to a
// Russian-browser visitor regardless of which locale page they land on.
---

<aside id="yandex-banner" class="yandex-banner" role="alert" hidden>
  <div class="yb-inner">
    <span class="yb-flag" aria-hidden="true">🇺🇦</span>
    <p class="yb-text">
      <span class="yb-line"
        >Yandex&nbsp;Browser — and any cooperation with russia — is not supported here.</span
      >
      <span class="yb-line yb-ua"
        >Яндекс&nbsp;Браузер — і будь-яка співпраця з росією — тут не підтримується.</span
      >
      <strong class="yb-slava">Slava Ukraini! 🇺🇦</strong>
    </p>
  </div>
</aside>

<script is:inline>
  // Yandex Browser puts "YaBrowser" in the UA string (alongside "Yowser").
  // Match it and reveal the banner. Inline so it runs on first parse, before
  // paint of the rest of the body — the banner is the first child of <body>.
  if (/YaBrowser/i.test(navigator.userAgent)) {
    var b = document.getElementById('yandex-banner');
    if (b) b.hidden = false;
  }
</script>

<style>
  /* Stays out of the layout entirely until the script un-hides it. */
  .yandex-banner[hidden] {
    display: none;
  }
  .yandex-banner {
    background: #0057b7; /* Ukrainian flag — blue */
    border-bottom: 4px solid #ffd700; /* Ukrainian flag — yellow */
    color: #fff;
  }
  .yb-inner {
    max-width: 72rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.85rem;
  }
  .yb-flag {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
    flex: 0 0 auto;
  }
  .yb-text {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-mono, ui-monospace, monospace);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.15rem;
  }
  .yb-ua {
    color: #ffd700;
  }
  .yb-slava {
    margin-top: 0.1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
</style>
